The paper deals with fingerprint recognition and spoof detection, which are primarily computer vision (cs.CV) and computer security (cs.CR) topics. The use of generative adversarial networks (GANs) for training the spoof detector also falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also involves image processing (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR) techniques.
